---
// AboutQuote.astro — Navy quote banner for the About page
---

<section class="about-quote">
  <div class="about-quote__inner">

    <blockquote class="about-quote__text" data-anim>
      "People might discount the need for a real trial attorney in family law —
      but the reality is that most people's first and only experience with the
      justice system is through family law. The need for a skilled trial attorney
      in your family law case is just as important as an other area of the law."
    </blockquote>

    <div class="about-quote__right-group" data-anim data-delay="1">
      <span class="about-quote__attribution">
        — Kyle McFarlane, Founding Partner
      </span>
      <a href="/contact" class="about-quote__cta">
        Schedule A Consultation
        <svg class="about-quote__cta-arrow" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 13L13 1M13 1H3M13 1V11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="about-quote__tagline" data-anim data-delay="1">
      RKKM Law represents clients who<br />cannot afford the wrong outcome. If<br />you've been referred to us, we're ready<br />to listen.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-quote {
    width: 100%;
    background: #1C2E4A;
    padding: 0 80px 56px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-quote__inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1280px;
    height: 536px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-quote__text {
    position: absolute;
    top: 72px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 140%;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #FAFAF9;
  }

  .about-quote__right-group {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: calc(40px + 2rem);
    right: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 6rem;
  }

  .about-quote__attribution {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 21px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #FAFAF9;
  }

  .about-quote__tagline {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 0;
    width: 280px;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 200%;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .about-quote__cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 16px;
    gap: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F0;
    width: fit-content;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 21px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #F0F0F0;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-quote__cta:hover {
    color: rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.7);
  }

  .about-quote__cta-arrow {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    color: #F0F0F0;
    display: inline-block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .about-quote__cta:hover .about-quote__cta-arrow {
    transform: translate(3px, -3px);
  }

  /* ---- Responsive ---- */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .about-quote { padding: 0 60px 56px; }
    .about-quote__text { font-size: 30px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-quote { padding: 0 40px 48px; }

    .about-quote__inner {
      height: auto;
      position: static;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 32px;
      padding-top: 64px;
    }

    .about-quote__text {
      position: static;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .about-quote__right-group {
      position: static;
    }

    .about-quote__tagline {
      position: static;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-quote { padding: 0 24px 40px; }
    .about-quote__text { font-size: 24px; }

    .about-quote__inner {
      padding-top: 48px;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-quote { padding: 0 16px 32px; }
    .about-quote__text { font-size: 20px; }
    .about-quote__inner { padding-top: 40px; }
  }
</style>
